OL,6,FA suicide support conference at St
OL,7,FPeter Port is aiming to reduce 's
OL,8,Fsubstantially high suicide rate.
OL,10,FThe two-day conference, organised by
OL,11,FTalking Benches, Guernsey Mind, and
OL,12,FGuernsey Samaritans, began today (7
