OL,6,FGuernsey Mind's chief executive Jo
OL,7,FCottell, said: "I couldn't say why the
OL,8,Fnumbers are higher (in Guernsey) but
OL,9,Fwhat we do need is to carry on the
OL,10,Fconversations on death and carry on
OL,11,Ftalking.
OL,13,F"That's why conferences like this are
OL,14,Fso important for us as an island and a
OL,15,Fcommunity."
