OL,6,FTalking Benches have been installed
OL,7,Faround the island to give people a
OL,8,Fsafe space to speak about their issues.
OL,10,FSuicide bereavement specialist Angela
OL,11,FSamata acknowledged it's a sign
OL,12,FGuernsey is moving in the right
OL,13,Fdirection.
OL,15,FShe explained: "I know (Guernsey) has
OL,16,Fthe talking benches which are such a
OL,17,Fgood idea and came from a place of
OL,18,Fpain from people who had experienced
OL,19,Fbereavement by suicide."
