OL,6,FLara Turner wishes more was done to
OL,7,Fhelp her father, Barry Jameson, who
OL,8,Ftook his own life two years ago.
OL,10,FLara said: "They say when you lose
OL,11,Fsomeone, you lose part of yourself; I
OL,12,Ffeel I still haven't found my new self
OL,13,Fyet so you just carry on going - you
OL,14,Fhave this huge void.
OL,16,F"With the mental health service, he
OL,17,Ftook his own life on the Sunday and he
OL,18,Fwas due an appointment on the Monday.
